    <section name="Quality control global tests">


     <p>User can add global tests to perform in this steps. The order of the parameters in the Aozan configuration
     file will be reused in the report generated by this step.  Each test can use
     several parameters and contains always an "<b>enable</b>" property to activate the test. Usually a property named "<b>interval</b>" exists
     for each test, however if this property is not set, the value will be computed but not checked if it is the correct interval.
     Usually the global tests reuse data collected from lane tests or sample tests. Please report to those documentation pages for more information. 
     You will find below all the parameters for all the available tests in Aozan:</p>

       <h4>Configuration global quality tests</h4>
       <table>
         <tr><th>Aozan property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default value</th><th>Description</th></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.globalrawclusters.enable</td><td>boolean</td><td>False</td><td>Enable global rawcluster test</td></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.globalrawclusters.interval</td><td>integer interval</td><td>False</td><td>Interval for valid values of global rawcluster</td></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.globalpfclusters.enable</td><td>boolean</td><td>False</td><td>Enable global pfcluster test</td></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.globalpfclusters.interval</td><td>integer interval</td><td>False</td><td>Interval for valid values of global pfclusters</td></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.globalpfclusterspercent.enable</td><td>boolean</td><td>False</td><td>Enable global pfclusterspercent test</td></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.globalpfclusterspercent.interval</td><td>double interval</td><td>False</td><td>Interval for valid values of global pfclusterspercent</td></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.globalbasecount.enable</td><td>boolean</td><td>False</td><td>Enable global base count test</td></tr>
         <tr><td>qc.test.nonindexedglobalbasecount.enable</td><td>boolean</td><td>False</td><td>Enable global non indexed global base count test</td></tr>
       </table>

       <p>An example of table built with lanes global tests.</p>
       <div align="center">
